     <div class="hmajors-01">
      <div class="hmajors-02">
       <div>
        <figure>
         <a href="https://today.appstate.edu/2019/03/06/sdap-ecrs">
          <picture>
           <source media="(max-width: 600px)" srcset="/_images/_posts/2019/03/sdap-ecrs-hmajors-0600.jpg"/>
           <source media="(max-width: 800px)" srcset="/_images/_posts/2019/03/sdap-ecrs-hmajors-0800.jpg"/>
           <source media="(max-width: 1000px)" srcset="/_images/_posts/2019/03/sdap-ecrs-hmajors-1000.jpg"/>
           <source media="(max-width: 1400px)" srcset="/_images/_posts/2019/03/sdap-ecrs-hmajors-1400.jpg"/>
           <img alt="Registering success" src="/_images/_posts/2019/03/sdap-ecrs-hmajors-2000.jpg"/>
          </picture>
         </a>
        </figure>
       </div>
      </div>
     </div>
     <div class="hmajors-03">
      <div class="hmajors-04">
       <div class="hmajors-05">
        <div>
         <div>
          <div class="hmajors-left">
           <div>
            <div class="hmajors-title">
             <a href="https://today.appstate.edu/2019/03/06/sdap-ecrs">
              Registering success
             </a>
            </div>
            <div class="hmajors-subtitle">
             <p>
              Appalachian State University’s SDAP partners with technology
              <span style="white-space: nowrap;">
               firm ECRS
              </span>
             </p>
            </div>
            <div class="hmajors-date">
             March 6, 2019
            </div>
           </div>
          </div>
          <div class="hmajors-right">
           <div>
            <div class="hmajors-teaser">
             <p>
              The Scholars with Diverse Abilities Program (SDAP) — a program designed to prepare college-age students with intellectual disabilities for personal growth and occupational success — has partnered with Boone-based technology firm ECR Software Corporation (ECRS) to create a mutually beneficial training program for SDAP students. The training program is part of an SDAP community access course, in which students learn both life and career skills.
             </p>
            </div>
           </div>
          </div>
         </div>
        </div>
       </div>
      </div>
     </div>
    </div>
