    <div class="hmajors-00 type-features hmajors-50 hmajors-overlay-dark hmajors-overlay-darker">
     <div class="hmajors-01">
      <div class="hmajors-02">
       <div>
        <figure>
         <a href="https://today.appstate.edu/2019/02/14/evans">
          <picture>
           <source media="(max-width: 600px)" srcset="/_images/_posts/2019/02/evans-hmajors-0600.jpg"/>
           <source media="(max-width: 800px)" srcset="/_images/_posts/2019/02/evans-hmajors-0800.jpg"/>
           <source media="(max-width: 1000px)" srcset="/_images/_posts/2019/02/evans-hmajors-1000.jpg"/>
           <source media="(max-width: 1400px)" srcset="/_images/_posts/2019/02/evans-hmajors-1400.jpg"/>
           <img alt="Dr. Sarah Evans makes hydrogeology studies relevant to everyday life" src="/_images/_posts/2019/02/evans-hmajors-2000.jpg"/>
          </picture>
         </a>
        </figure>
       </div>
      </div>
     </div>
     <div class="hmajors-03">
      <div class="hmajors-04">
       <div class="hmajors-05">
        <div>
         <div>
          <div class="hmajors-left">
           <div>
            <div class="hmajors-title">
             <a href="https://today.appstate.edu/2019/02/14/evans">
              Dr. Sarah Evans makes hydrogeology studies relevant
              <span style="white-space: nowrap;">
               to everyday life
              </span>
             </a>
            </div>
            <div class="hmajors-date">
             Feb. 14, 2019
            </div>
           </div>
          </div>
          <div class="hmajors-right">
           <div>
            <div class="hmajors-teaser">
             <p>
              Dr. Sarah Evans never wants her lectures to be dry — particularly since her subject is water: its movement, quality and interactions on and below the Earth’s surface. “My job, as a professor, is to get students excited about the topic,” Evans said. “Why do we care about water? No matter what our education level is or whether or not we’re interested in science, water is something that affects everyone.”
             </p>
            </div>
           </div>
          </div>
         </div>
        </div>
       </div>
      </div>
     </div>
